creator: v2
descriptionHtml:
Thanks for playing Happy Pixel Farm!


Please provide feedback for future releases thanks.

❤️How to play:
- Select the planting ground/soil and select an item to plant.
- Drag the seed bag towards the soil area.
- Click on cows to harvest their milk.

❤️Info:
- Click the barn to pop-up cow buying panel.
- Click the soil ground to pop-up buying seeds panel.

❤️Future updates:
- C̶o̶w̶s̶ ̶(̶f̶o̶r̶ ̶p̶r̶o̶d̶u̶c̶i̶n̶g̶ ̶m̶i̶l̶k̶)̶.̶
- Chicken (For producing eggs).
- Bakery (turn your milk and eggs into variety of pastries).
- W̶a̶n̶d̶e̶r̶i̶n̶g̶ ̶N̶P̶C̶ ̶f̶o̶r̶ ̶q̶u̶e̶s̶t̶s̶/̶m̶i̶s̶s̶i̶o̶n̶s̶.̶
descriptionShort: Manage your small little farm in this cute pixel art game!
